songs.title: Lonely Star
songs.lyrics:
Letra de Lonely Star[Verso 1]
In my lonely star
I remember you
I see in your love
In my lonely star
I cry
You know, you know i cry

[Verso 2]
Ahhh, I will follow you
Ahhh, you will talk to me
Ahhh, I will reach to you
Ahhh, I will kiss you so
But now i cry
You know, you know i cry

[Otro]
Darling, i need you
